data.description: Great STARTER HOME! 3 bedroom,1 bath RANCH on a spacious lot with a two car garage & excellent curb appeal. Lennox High Efficiency Furnace and A/C Unit.Carpeted Living room is spacious with sunlight streaming in, vinyl tilt-in windows and coat closet. Eat-In updated kitchen, nice countertops, stain resistant double sink & GE Dishwasher.Appliances are staying.Side by Side Refrigerator, Gas Oven. All three bedrooms have hard wood flooring, overhead lighting and generous closet space. Home updated bath with ceramic tile flooring,with newer (2020) modern vanity and hallway linen closet. Partially finished lower level has to two large rooms.Vinyl floored family room 14X 23 and a laundry /storage room 25 by 21. Low maintenance landscaping & lawn care all trees have been removed.Includes newer Vinyl windows throughout. Move in Ready.
